TextEng: "Do you know where I could get some equipment?"
"Why are all these people in here?"
Text: "왜 이 사람들이 다 여기 있는 거죠?"

TextEng: "Gold help me too. You give me gold or goodbye widows and orphans."
Text: "금화 나도 도움 돼. 금화 줘 안 그러면 과부들이랑 고아들 안녕."

TextEng: "Gold would help me as well. You don't want anything to happen to these poor widows and orphans?"
Text: "금화는 저한테도 도움이 될 거예요. 이 불쌍한 과부들과 고아들에게 무슨 일이 생기길 원하진 않으시겠죠?"

TextEng: "Me no care. Give me you gold."
"I don't care. Give me your gold."
"Me guess me no help you then."
"I guess I can't help you then."
"Ha! Me guess you find calling in life at young age."
Text: "하! 어릴 때 인생 목표 찾았나 봐."

TextEng: "Ha! I guess you found your calling in life early."
"Me guess you do what you must to live."
"I guess you do what you have to, to survive."
"That be awful. How you do bad thing like that?"
Text: "그거 끔찍해. 어떻게 그런 나쁜 짓 해?"

TextEng: "That is horrible! How could you do such things?"
Text: "끔찍하네요! 어떻게 그런 일을 할 수 있죠?"

TextEng: "Me want help you with widows and orphans."
Text: "나 과부들이랑 고아들 돕는 거 도와주고 싶어."

TextEng: "I would like to help you with the widows and orphans."
